node.title: Cordons set up as police search for a man in Mt Maunganui
node.description: Police are asking some residents to stay indoors as they try and locate a man in the central area of Mount Maunganui.
node.content:
["Police are asking some residents to stay indoors as they try and locate a man in the central area of Mount Maunganui.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "They said in a statement that they are attending a serious incident in the Bedford Place area.", "There are concerns for the wellbeing of the man who police are now trying to find.", "As a precaution, an area has been cordoned off, and residents have been asked to stay indoors."]
